# Screen & UI Patterns

- Screens are `StatelessWidget` (or `StatefulWidget` for auth/forms).
- Async UI uses `switch (controller.requestStatus)` with shimmer/error/loaded states.
- Loading placeholders: dedicated `*_Shimmer.dart` widgets per section.
- Images: `CustomCachedNetworkImage`; icons: `CustomSvgPicture`.
- Forms: `GlobalKey<FormState>` + inline validators on `CustomTextFromField`.
- Push detail screens with model args: `NewsDetailsScreen(model: article)`.
- Bottom nav lives in `MainScreen`; tab bodies swapped via `setState`.
